# DevOps Assignment

This project is a simple DevOps deployment of a FastAPI application on AWS EC2 using Docker Compose.

# Technologies

- AWS EC2
- Ubuntu
- Docker
- Docker Compose
- FastAPI
- NGINX
- PostgreSQL
- Redis

# Project Structure

```
app/
nginx/
docker-compose.yml
README.md
```

# Start the project

```
docker compose up -d --build
```

To stop the project

```
docker compose down
```

Check running containers

```
docker ps
```

## Running Services

- NGINX - Port 80
- FastAPI - Port 8000
- PostgreSQL - Port 5432
- Redis - Port 6379

